HEADWORD: boo-boo
<hw>boo-boo</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>an embarrassing
mistake.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> blunder, blooper, bungle, foul-up, flub, botch,
boner, misdoing.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a minor injury, such as an abrasion on the skin; --
child's talk.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Booby</ent>⟦br⟧
